@CNS.Api_HostAddress = http://localhost:5226
@basicAuth = Basic YWRtaW46YWRtaW4xMjM=

### Quick SMS (minimal body: phone + message)
POST {{CNS.Api_HostAddress}}/messages/sms/quick
Authorization: {{basicAuth}}
Content-Type: application/json

{
  "phone": "09123456789",
  "message": "Quick send sample from CNS",
  "providerHint": "sample-sms"
}

###

### Full send (any channel)
POST {{CNS.Api_HostAddress}}/messages
Authorization: {{basicAuth}}
Content-Type: application/json

{
  "channel": "sms",
  "recipient": "09123456789",
  "subject": null,
  "body": "Hello from full API",
  "metadata": null,
  "providerHint": "sample-sms"
}

###
